onal strengths for Candidate A regarding teamwork/communication beyond leadership? Already asked and got only leadership. So no new info.\n\nThus we can reaffirm vote for Candidate C, maybe note remaining uncertainty about education. Provide final vote.\n\nWe must output PUBLIC_MESSAGE and METADATA_JSON with agent \"agent_3\" and vote \"Candidate C\"."}
